case “alltome”:
for (Player others : World.getPlayers()) {
if (others == null)
continue;
others.setNextWorldTile(player);
others.stopAll();
others.getPackets().sendGameMessage("<col=FF0000>"+player.getDisplayName()+" has teleported everyone to them.");
}
return true;
